title: ‘Unidentified Flying Object’ Seen as SpaceX Rocket Exploded?
subtitle: Video capturing the explosion of SpaceX’s Falcon-9 rocket during a test fire seems to show an unidentified flying object pass above the rocket just beforehand.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: An unidentified flying object passes above SpaceX’s Falcon-9 rocket at the same moment it explodes, suggesting the rocket’s destruction was intentional.
